# COCS 314 Project

## Student Information
Name: YOUR NAME
Course: COCS 314

## Project Title
Vendors Unite

## Project Description
This project is a web-based application created for the COCS 314 Web Programming course. The website allows users to interact with a vendor marketplace system using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Features include adding items to a cart, displaying products, and interactive page elements using DOM manipulation and JavaScript events.

The project demonstrates understanding of:
- HTML page structure
- CSS styling
- JavaScript functions
- DOM manipulation
- Event handling
- Arrays and user interaction

## How To Run The Project
1. Download the project files
   2. Open the folder
3. Double-click index.html
4. The website will open in your browser

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
